import React from "react";
import { Form,Row,Col,Container, ListGroup } from 'react-bootstrap'

export default function ListaPazienti() {
    return (
        <Container>
            <Row>
                <Col>
                    <Form inline>
                        <FormControl type="text" placeholder="Mario Rossi" className="mr-sm-2" />
                        <Button variant="outline-success">Search</Button>
                    </Form>
                </Col>
            </Row>
            <Row>
                <Col>
                    <ListGroup>
                        <ListGroup.Item>Cardiospirina</ListGroup.Item>
                        <ListGroup.Item>Moment</ListGroup.Item>
                        <ListGroup.Item>Tachipirina</ListGroup.Item>
                        <ListGroup.Item>Fermenti</ListGroup.Item>
                        <ListGroup.Item>Xanax</ListGroup.Item>
                    </ListGroup>
                </Col>
            </Row>
        </Container>

    );
}
